Blockbuster Entertainment Corp said itagreed to buy &lt;Southern Video>, a Blockbuster licensee in SanAntonio.    Blockbuster said it will issue 80,460 shares of its commonstock for all the net assets of Southern Video.    The company said after the acquisition is complete, itintends to open additional Blockbuster Video Superstores in theSan Antonio market. Reuter&#3;